OL,3,CGovernment should 'recognise enormity
OL,4,Cof threat' on Jewish communities, MP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFormer Liverpool Riverside MP and the
OL,8,FChair of the Board of Deputies of
OL,9,FBritish Jews is urging the Government
OL,10,Fto "recognise the enormity of the
OL,11,Fthreat" on Jewish communities after a
OL,12,Fseries of recent attacks.
OL,14,FIt comes after two men were stabbed in
OL,15,Fa terrorist incident in Golders Green
OL,16,Fin North London.
OL,18,FThe stabbing was the second declared
OL,19,Fterror attack on the Jewish community
OL,20,Fin the UK in just seven months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
