PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777593772
OL,3,CGovernment should 'recognise enormity
OL,4,Cof threat' on Jewish communities, MP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIn October, Melvin Cravitz and Adrian
OL,8,FDaulby were killed at the Heaton Park
OL,9,Fsynagogue in Crumpsall, Manchester
OL,10,Fwhen 35-year-old Jihad Al-Shamie drove
OL,11,Finto the gates of the place of worship
OL,12,Fand launched a knife attack.
OL,14,FThe former MP says that it is now a
OL,15,Fnational emergency and more needs to
OL,16,Fbe done to tackle antisemitism.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777593772
OL,3,CGovernment should 'recognise enormity
OL,4,Cof threat' on Jewish communities, MP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FLouise Ellman said: "Members of the
OL,8,FJewish community have warned very
OL,9,Floudly and very strongly about the
OL,10,Ffear that was around, about the
OL,11,Fconcern that was building up, yet very
OL,12,Flittle was done.
OL,14,F"And now we see people actually being
OL,15,Fattacked and stabbed on the streets of
OL,16,Fthis country in London, in Golders
OL,17,FGreen, simply for being Jews and that
OL,18,Fjust can't be allowed to go on."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777593772
OL,3,CGovernment should 'recognise enormity
OL,4,Cof threat' on Jewish communities, MP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe continued: "I feel extremely
OL,8,Fdisturbed. I feel that something
OL,9,Ffundamental has changed in this
OL,10,Fcountry in relation to the Jewish
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"I've been involved in issues fighting
OL,14,Fanti-Semitism for a very long time,
OL,15,Fbut somehow it feels different now.
OL,17,F"I feel there's something different
OL,18,Fabout it and that somehow the
OL,19,FGovernment, while it is taking action
OL,20,Fand has taken action, hasn't fully
OL,21,Frecognised the enormity of the threat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777593772
OL,3,CGovernment should 'recognise enormity
OL,4,Cof threat' on Jewish communities, MP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"And we've never before seen people
OL,8,Fkilled, murdered in Heaton Park
OL,9,FSynagogue and now on the streets of
OL,10,FLondon in Golders Green, so I feel
OL,11,Fextremely uneasy but very concerned.
OL,13,F"The government is right to increase
OL,14,Fsecurity and it has done that and it's
OL,15,Falso looking at new legislation which
OL,16,Fis just going through Parliament."
OL,18,FWhile the former MP says the
OL,19,FGovernment's decision is right and
OL,20,Fvery much welcomed, she says that it
OL,21,Fwill not be enough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1777593772
OL,3,CGovernment should 'recognise enormity
OL,4,Cof threat' on Jewish communities, MP
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I think a line has been crossed now
OL,8,Fand I think we now have to look in a
OL,9,Fmuch more fundamental way about how
OL,10,Fthe incitement to hate and to kill
OL,11,FJews to this level has come about in
OL,12,Fthis country, and we have to look at
OL,13,Fwhere that incitement comes from."
OL,15,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,16,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,17,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,18,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
